# Security Policy

## Supported Versions

| Library                                                | Version | Supported          |
|--------------------------------------------------------|---------|--------------------|
| [NodeJS](https://github.com/nodejs/node)               | 20.19.1 | :white_check_mark: |
| [TypeScript](https://github.com/microsoft/typescript)  | 5.9.3   | :white_check_mark: |
| [React](https://github.com/facebook/react)             | 19.2.3  | :white_check_mark: |
